{"type":"message","id":"4deb5be7","parentId":"32d08f3a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T11:03:26.129Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2soiq8rbr55w_1","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 1,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775041399932,\n      \"sessionId\": \"fb9f485f-725c-42b6-8d46-028bc8ac4f6a\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 49227,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/fb9f485f-725c-42b6-8d46-028bc8ac4f6a.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check if there are active sessions first.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_2soiq8rbr55w_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"activeMinutes\": 5,\n                \"messageLimit\": 1\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775041400417\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":1,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775041399932,"sessionId":"fb9f485f-725c-42b6-8d46-028bc8ac4f6a","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":49227,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/fb9f485f-725c-42b6-8d46-028bc8ac4f6a.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check if there are active sessions first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2soiq8rbr55w_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775041400417}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775041406113}}
{"type":"message","id":"353b95d5","parentId":"4deb5be7","timestamp":"2026-04-01T11:03:30.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the current cron session itself. There are no other active user sessions in the last 5 minutes. So I should execute the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me:\n1. Search for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services\n2. Organize 3-5 key pieces of information\n3. Save to the memory file\n\nLet me read the miaoda-web-search skill first.","thinkingSignature":"95a7cca3abaf28eab02186d363cf2c764c7df7d5987d7024c7f3afa8d37db1b2"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前cron会话本身，无其他活跃用户对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_034eu6c7zcgd_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":816,"output":152,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44949,"cost":{"input":0.0002448,"output":0.0001824,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017466299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775041406129}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca6b2be5","parentId":"353b95d5","timestamp":"2026-04-01T11:03:30.218Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_034eu6c7zcgd_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775041410215}}
{"type":"message","id":"06fba18e","parentId":"ca6b2be5","timestamp":"2026-04-01T11:03:35.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for relevant industry news using the web search skill. I'll search for several topics related to Daojian Network's business.","thinkingSignature":"e223b808b528443b9caa147bca2d1ae832ebd5e036f506e904ebca6c655b5130"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9zor1sb7tw6l_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新动态 政策\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9zor1sb7tw6l_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026发展趋势\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9zor1sb7tw6l_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9zor1sb7tw6l_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 政企解决方案 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1483,"output":262,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45726,"cost":{"input":0.00044489999999999997,"output":0.0003144,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00207873}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775041410218}}
